      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON ZIRCONIA (2) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 4.5 lengths into third (23.46) at this track in a Grade 6 over 400m. Sure to be about the mark. CINTA'S ME MUM (4) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at this track over 305m behind Shanny Rose (18.28) in a Grade 6. Was a winner the start prior. Should play a prominent role. EXTRAVAGANTLY (8) should enjoy clear running from the outside box. Below best latest at Angle Park (20.51) when 6th and beaten 10 lengths. Form here at this distance is strong including three wins. Worth following up. MISTY AUTUMN (1) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
